                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "He thought that Russia was supporting the Cuban Revolution with atomic weapons and military supplies."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "He thought that Russia was covertly supporting communist groups in the United States."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "He thought that Russia was competing with China for influence over Third World nations."
